  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to your new calming career path!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fishtronomy</strong> is a short <i>adorable</i> casual cozy puzzle game about guiding fish through space and completing constellations! It's your first day as a 'junior Fishtronomer' and together with your new partner <i>Phebe</i>, it's your job to help decorate the night sky. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple and Satisfying!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a mouse to fling <i>'Star Fish'</i> across space, teleport them through wormholes, find keys to open new pathways, and form unique constellations. Fishtronomy aims to have accessible, simple, minimalistic gameplay while still being fun and interesting to play. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644080/extras/dede8442bd0f0457ea53a531f71fd04a.poster.avif?t=1752112944\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644080/extras/dede8442bd0f0457ea53a531f71fd04a.webm?t=1752112944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644080/extras/dede8442bd0f0457ea53a531f71fd04a.mp4?t=1752112944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore galaxies (and beyond)!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fishtronomy consists of 3 'galaxy sets' each filled with different kinds of constellations. Some large, some small - but all unique in their own small way.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to your new calming career path!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fishtronomy</strong> is a short <i>adorable</i> casual cozy puzzle game about guiding fish through space and completing constellations! It's your first day as a 'junior Fishtronomer' and together with your new partner <i>Phebe</i>, it's your job to help decorate the night sky. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple and Satisfying!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a mouse to fling <i>'Star Fish'</i> across space, teleport them through wormholes, find keys to open new pathways, and form unique constellations. Fishtronomy aims to have accessible, simple, minimalistic gameplay while still being fun and interesting to play. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644080/extras/dede8442bd0f0457ea53a531f71fd04a.poster.avif?t=1752112944\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644080/extras/dede8442bd0f0457ea53a531f71fd04a.webm?t=1752112944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644080/extras/dede8442bd0f0457ea53a531f71fd04a.mp4?t=1752112944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore galaxies (and beyond)!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fishtronomy consists of 3 'galaxy sets' each filled with different kinds of constellations. Some large, some small - but all unique in their own small way.</p>",
